adding\"><div class=\"fg-row row    \" ><div class=\"ffb-id-47cfqqtj fg-col col-xs-12 col-md-12 fg-text-dark\"><h1 class=\"ffb-id-47cfrfga fg-heading text-center    fg-text-dark\">TR\u1ea2I NGHI\u1ec6M TH\u00c2N THI\u1ec6N V\u1edaI M\u00d4I TR\u01af\u1edcNG<\/h1><div class=\"ffb-id-47cfuio1 fg-paragraph ff-richtext text-left    fg-text-dark\"><\/p>\n<p>T\u1ea1i Caravelle Saigon, ch&uacute;ng t&ocirc;i \u01b0u ti&ecirc;n c&aacute;c ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng th&acirc;n thi\u1ec7n v\u1edbi m&ocirc;i tr\u01b0\u1eddng, t\u1ef1 h&agrave;o l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn c&aacute;c gi\u1ea3i ph&aacute;p thay th\u1ebf b\u1ec1n v\u1eefng trong m\u1ecdi kh&iacute;a c\u1ea1nh ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ee7a m&igrave;nh.<\/p>\n<p>H&agrave;nh \u0111\u1ed9ng xanh c\u1ee7a ch&uacute;ng t&ocirc;i l&agrave; m\u1ed9t c&aacute;ch ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn th&acirc;n thi\u1ec7n v\u1edbi m&ocirc;i tr\u01b0\u1eddng b\u1eb1ng c&aacute;ch cung c\u1ea5p c&aacute;c s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m t\u1eafm c&oacute; th\u1ec3 t&aacute;i s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng, s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng b&agrave;n ch\u1ea3i, l\u01b0\u1ee3c v&agrave; dao c\u1ea1o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l&agrave;m t\u1eeb v\u1ecf l&uacute;a m&igrave;, s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng bao b&igrave; t&aacute;i ch\u1ebf, khuy\u1ebfn kh&iacute;ch t&aacute;i s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng d&eacute;p, khuy\u1ebfn kh&iacute;ch kh&aacute;ch l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn t&aacute;i s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng v\u1ea3i lanh. Cam k\u1ebft th&acirc;n thi\u1ec7n v\u1edbi m&ocirc;i tr\u01b0\u1eddng n&agrave;y nh\u1ea5n m\u1ea1nh s\u1ef1 c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn c\u1ee7a ch&uacute;ng t&ocirc;i cho tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m kh&aacute;ch s\u1ea1n xanh h\u01a1n, c&oacute; tr&aacute;ch nhi\u1ec7m h\u01a1n.<\/p>\n<div id=\"gtx-trans\" style=\"position: absolute;left: 142px;top: -13.0994px\">\n<div class=\"gtx-trans-icon\">&nbsp;<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<p><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/section><style>.ffb-id-47cfqqti{ padding-top: 10px;padding-right: 30px;padding-bottom: 10px;padding-left: 30px;}@media (min-width:768px) { .ffb-id-47cfqqti{ padding-top: 30px;pa